{"type":"article_comment","id":13616,"parentType":"article","parentId":2227,"uid":4516,"contents":"坦克碾人的实证有被轧断双腿的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/方政\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">方政</a>。<br>\n六四清场的血腥图片，我在<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200413030004/https://blog.boxun.com/hero/64/52_1.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>收藏下来了。注意真的很血腥。<br>\n<br>\n用这首歌纪念那些为着民主死去的人们：《<a href=\"https://listenonrepeat.com/watch/?v=9L_qz7LuqVU#《自由花》MV-「六四」二十周年製作%E3%80%82\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自由花</a>》<br>\n<br>\n上面是listenonrepeat.com的链接，原来youtube的视频被人加了<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9L_qz7LuqVU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">年龄限制</a>。给法西斯洗地非蠢即坏，知道六四的真相仍然洗地，又蠢又坏。","date":"2020-06-03","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}